gomodel:SYNGO_5037  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Figure 3: reverse IP of mGluR1a (GRM1) and TRPC1 in HEK-293 cells and additional TRPC1 pulldown in hippocampi showed these proteins can interact.\n\nFigure 6: in stratum interneurons, siRNA knockdown of TRPC1 reduced the amplitude of slow EPSCs.. Experimental description: M&M: \"Organotypic hippocampal slice cultures were prepared from 7 to 12 days old rats and biolistically co-transfected with a plasmid for EYFP expression and siRNAs as previously described\"" ;
